column5: Hit Lake Erie today...it's still on fire!  Got an 18 fish limit again.  Dipsy and leadcore with spinners were the hot ticket.
nice wish I lived closer, to fish it  oh well I have simcoe guess I shouldn't complain
Well done boys !!!!  18 !!! Sounds like you guys were very busy ? Those 2 you are holding are brutes !!!     Cheers
more walleye curtains. Nice stuff... looks like nice day too
Wow Doug, that's some good fishing!
